# Macro Map — import-script credentials.
# Copy this file to ".env" (which is git-ignored) and fill in real values.
# The service_role key is SECRET and bypasses Row-Level Security — keep it local,
# never commit it, never put it in client-side code (js/config.js).
#
# Find these in Supabase → Project Settings → API Keys:
#   - SUPABASE_URL                : your Project URL
#   - SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY   : the "service_role" secret key

